    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zozo and The Lost Dreams is a 2D Metroidvania platformer inspired by classic Sunday-morning cartoons.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter Zozo’s Dream</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Zozo, a 13-year-old boy who dreams of becoming a superhero— literally and figuratively. Through the help of Zozo’s mad scientist neighbor, Professor Aisha, Zozo is able to enter his dreams and live out his fantasy of becoming a superhero. However, a strange incident prevents him from waking up! Zozo must now go on an adventure to find his way back home. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/e4d5a4c808ec706b3180d58b362ef34d.poster.avif?t=1770864821\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/e4d5a4c808ec706b3180d58b362ef34d.webm?t=1770864821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/e4d5a4c808ec706b3180d58b362ef34d.mp4?t=1770864821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore Imaginative and Vibrant World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re in the mood for scaling mountainous cupcakes or eliminating predatory computer ‘bugs’, each dream has its own distinct visuals and theme inspired by various cartoon tropes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/000341e763e41191424af479f79b628f.poster.avif?t=1770864821\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/000341e763e41191424af479f79b628f.webm?t=1770864821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/000341e763e41191424af479f79b628f.mp4?t=1770864821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make New Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In his journey, Zozo encounters many faces— both friendly and otherwise. Aid them in their quirky hijinks and form lasting bonds. Work together with a colorful cast of characters to uncover a sinister plot that threatens to take away all of Zozo’s dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/497ecbd8fb67e37fcc65ad052b1b2dce.poster.avif?t=1770864821\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/497ecbd8fb67e37fcc65ad052b1b2dce.webm?t=1770864821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230120/extras/497ecbd8fb67e37fcc65ad052b1b2dce.mp4?t=1770864821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
